Text.CultureInvariantString:
THE THIRD DATA CENTRE 
LAY AHEAD OF THE 
BAND OF MISCREANTS

ONCE AGAIN 
THE WRETCHED 
RODENT 
PREPARED TO 
SCUTTLE THROUGH.

HOWEVER 
THE GUARDS 
WOULD NOW 
CERTAINLY 
APPREHENDED 
THEIR PREY

HAVING RECENTLY 
UNDERGONE EXTENSIVE 
TRAINING IN THEIR 
CORE COMPETENCIES
